te": "2025-11-01", "dateLabelColor": "#0969da"}, "P5": {"htmlDir": "docs/post/5.html", "labels": ["Post"], "postTitle": "\u4e09\u4e2d\u975e\u60c5\u666f\u5f0f\u559c\u5267  \u7b2c\u4e8c\u5e55\u2014\u2014\u9999\u96ea", "postUrl": "post/5.html", "postSourceUrl": "https://github.com/10086Coda10086/10086Coda10086.github.io/issues/5", "commentNum": 0, "wordCount": 2147, "description": "## \u7b2c\u4e8c\u5e55\uff08\u4e0a\uff09\n\n\u200b\t\u5728\u52a0\u4e86\u5979\u7684\u5fae\u4fe1\u540e\uff0c\u4ed6\u51e0\u4e4e\u6ca1\u6709\u548c\u5979\u8bf4\u8fc7\u4e00\u53e5\u8bdd\uff0c\u53ea\u662f\u4e92\u76f8\u786e\u8ba4\u4e86\u540d\u5b57\u3002", "top": 0, "createdAt": 1761985072, "style": "", "script": "<script src='https://blog.meekdai.com/Gmeek/plugins/articletoc.js'></script><script src='https://blog.meekdai.com/Gmeek/plugins/lightbox.js'></script>", "head": "", "ogImage": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/103094747?s=400&u=54690c656e8bf740633710628214ac5a495f4838&v=4", "createdDate": "2025-11-01", "dateLabelColor": "#0969da"}, "P6": {"htmlDir": "docs/post/6.html", "labels": ["softwares"], "postTitle": "\u3010\u5b9e\u6218\u8bb0\u5f55\u3011\u96f6\u57fa\u7840\u7f16\u7a0b\uff1f\u6211\u5982\u4f55\u5b8c\u5168\u9760AI\u5f00\u53d1\u4e86\u4e00\u6b3e\u5b89\u5353\u624b\u8868\u5e94\u7528", "postUrl": "post/6.html", "postSourceUrl": "https://github.com/10086Coda10086/10086Coda10086.github.io/issues/6", "commentNum": 0, "wordCount": 2342, "description": "**\u6458\u8981**\uff1a\u6ca1\u6709\u7f16\u7a0b\u57fa\u7840\uff0c\u4e0d\u61c2 Java \u6216 Kotlin\uff0c\u751a\u81f3\u8fde Android Studio \u7684\u754c\u9762\u90fd\u770b\u4e0d\u61c2\u3002", "top": 0, "createdAt": 1763827315, "style": "", "script": "<script src='https://blog.meekdai.com/Gmeek/plugins/articletoc.js'></script><script src='https://blog.meekdai.com/Gmeek/plugins/lightbox.js'></script>", "head": "", "ogImage": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/103094747?s=400&u=54690c656e8bf740633710628214ac5a495f4838&v=4", "createdDate": "2025-11-23", "dateLabelColor": "#0969da"}, "P7": {"htmlDir": "docs/post/7.html", "labels": ["softwares"], "postTitle": "\u4ece\u96f6\u5f00\u59cb\u7684\u5c0f\u4e3b\u673a\u6298\u817e\u673a#1", "postUrl": "post/7.html", "postSourceUrl": "https://github.com/10086Coda10086/10086Coda10086.github.io/issues/7", "commentNum": 0, "wordCount": 11382, "description": "\u4f7f\u7528\u8bbe\u5907\uff1a\u60e0\u666e t628\n\n![Image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/97c14621-6236-4908-8d65-d89638e65bc1)\n\n\u5b89\u5b89\u9759\u9759\u5730\u8eba\u5728\u6211\u7684\u4e66\u67dc\u4e0a\n\n## 1. \u5b89\u88c5\u7cfb\u7edf\n\n\u53ef\u7528\u4e8e\u5bb6\u7528\u670d\u52a1\u5668\u7684\u7cfb\u7edf\u9009\u62e9\u5176\u5b9e\u5f88\u591a\u3002", "top": 0, "createdAt": 1770042055, "style": "", "script": "<script src='https://blog.meekdai.com/Gmeek/plugins/articletoc.js'></script><script src='https://blog.meekdai.com/Gmeek/plugins/lightbox.js'></script>", "head": "", "ogImage": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/103094747?s=400&u=54690c656e8bf740633710628214ac5a495f4838&v=4", "createdDate": "2026-02-02", "dateLabelColor": "#1f883d"}, "P8": {"htmlDir": "docs/post/8.html", "labels": ["softwares"], "postTitle": "\u4ece\u96f6\u5f00\u59cb\u7684\u5c0f\u4e3b\u673a\u6298\u817e\u8bb0#2", "postUrl": "post/8.html", "postSourceUrl": "https://github.com/10086Coda10086/10086Coda10086.github.io/issues/8", "commentNum": 0, "wordCount": 8865, "description": "# \u4ece\u96f6\u5f00\u59cb\u7684\u5c0f\u4e3b\u673a\u6298\u817e\u8bb0#2\n\n## \u7eed\u4e0a\u4e00\u7ae0\uff1aDocker \u76f8\u5173\u4e8b\u9879\u8865\u5145\n\n\u4e0a\u4e00\u7ae0\u4e2d\u5173\u4e8e Docker \u7684\u5185\u5bb9\u76f8\u5bf9\u504f\u591a\uff0c\u5982\u679c\u5bf9 Docker \u8fd8\u4e0d\u592a\u719f\u6089\uff0c\u53ef\u4ee5\u5148\u7528\u4e0b\u9762\u8fd9\u4e2a**\u6700\u7b80\u5355\u7684\u9a8c\u8bc1\u4e0e\u8865\u6551\u65b9\u6cd5**\u3002", "top": 0, "createdAt": 1770124779, "style": "", "script": "<script src='https://blog.meekdai.com/Gmeek/plugins/articletoc.js'></script><script src='https://blog.meekdai.com/Gmeek/plugins/lightbox.js'></script>", "head": "", "ogImage": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/103094747?s=400&u=54690c656e8bf740633710628214ac5a495f4838&v=4", "createdDate": "2026-02-03", "dateLabelColor": "#1f883d"}, "P9": {"htmlDir": "docs/post/9.html", "labels": ["softwares"], "postTitle": "\u4ece\u96f6\u5f00\u59cb\u7684\u5c0f\u4e3b\u673a\u6298\u817e\u8bb0#3", "postUrl": "post/9.html", "postSourceUrl": "https://github.com/10086Coda10086/10086Coda10086.github.io/issues/9", "commentNum": 0, "wordCount": 3933, "description": "\u662f\u65f6\u5019\u628a\u5b83\u6539\u9020\u6210NAS\u4e86\uff01\n\n## \u4e00\u3001NAS-Panel\n\n**NAS-Panel \u2260 \u4f20\u7edf NAS \u7cfb\u7edf\uff08\u5982 TrueNAS\uff09**\n \u5b83\u662f\u4e00\u4e2a\uff1a\n\n- \ud83e\udded Web \u7ba1\u7406\u9762\u677f\n- \ud83d\udce6 \u96c6\u6210 Docker \u7ba1\u7406\n- \ud83d\udcc1 \u5e26\u6587\u4ef6\u7ba1\u7406\u529f\u80fd\n- \ud83d\udcbe \u53ef\u7ba1\u7406\u6302\u8f7d\u7684\u78c1\u76d8\uff08\u5982 `/data`\uff09\n\n**\u975e\u5e38\u9002\u5408\u4f60\u8fd9\u79cd\uff1a**\n\n> \u5c0f\u4e3b\u673a + Ubuntu Server + Docker + \u5355\u5757\u5927\u5bb9\u91cf\u673a\u68b0\u76d8\n\n------\n\n### \u4e8c\u3001\u90e8\u7f72\u524d\u68c0\u67e5\uff08\u5f88\u91cd\u8981\uff0c\u907f\u514d\u540e\u9762\u62a5\u9519\uff09\n\n#### 1\ufe0f\u20e3 \u786e\u8ba4 Docker \u6b63\u5e38\n\n```\ndocker version\n```\n\n\u80fd\u770b\u5230 Client / Server \u4fe1\u606f\u5373\u53ef\u3002", "top": 0, "createdAt": 1770171156, "style": "", "script": "<script src='https://blog.meekdai.com/Gmeek/plugins/articletoc.js'></script><script src='https://blog.meekdai.com/Gmeek/plugins/lightbox.js'></script>", "head": "", "ogImage": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/103094747?s=400&u=54690c656e8bf740633710628214ac5a495f4838&v=4", "createdDate": "2026-02-04", "dateLabelColor": "#1f883d"}, "P10": {"htmlDir": "docs/post/10.html", "labels": ["softwares"], "postTitle": "\u4ece\u96f6\u5f00\u59cb\u7684\u5c0f\u4e3b\u673a\u6298\u817e\u8bb0#4 \u2014\u2014Samba", "postUrl": "post/10.html", "postSourceUrl": "https://github.com/10086Coda10086/10086Coda10086.github.io/issues/10", "commentNum": 0, "wordCount": 3588, "description": "\u8fdb\u4e00\u6b65\u914d\u7f6e\u6210NAS\n\n## \u4e00\u3001Samba\u5e72\u4ec0\u4e48\n\n1. **Linux \u4e0a\u6709\u4e00\u4e2a\u771f\u5b9e\u5b58\u5728\u7684\u76ee\u5f55**\uff08\u6bd4\u5982 `/data`\uff09\n2. **Samba \u628a\u8fd9\u4e2a\u76ee\u5f55\u201c\u5171\u4eab\u201d\u51fa\u53bb**\n3. **Windows \u901a\u8fc7 SMB \u534f\u8bae\u8bbf\u95ee**\n\n------\n\n## \u4e8c\u3001\u786e\u8ba4\u6570\u636e\u76d8\u72b6\u6001\uff08\u5fc5\u987b\u5148\u5bf9\uff09\n\n### 2.1 \u786e\u8ba4 `/data` \u5df2\u6302\u8f7d\n\n```\nlsblk\n```\n\n\u4f60\u5e94\u8be5\u770b\u5230\u7c7b\u4f3c\uff1a\n\n```\nsdb\n\u2514\u2500sdb1  465G  /data\n```\n\n#### \u274c \u5e38\u89c1\u9519\u8bef\n\n- **\u6ca1\u770b\u5230 `/data`**\n  - \u8bf4\u660e\u6ca1\u6302\u8f7d\u6210\u529f\n  - Samba \u5171\u4eab\u201c\u7a7a\u6c14\u201d\uff0cWindows \u4e00\u5b9a\u8fde\u4e0d\u4e0a\n\n\ud83d\udc49 \u5982\u679c\u6ca1\u6302\u8f7d\uff0c**\u5148\u522b\u7ee7\u7eed**\n\n------\n\n### 2.2 \u786e\u8ba4\u76ee\u5f55\u771f\u5b9e\u5b58\u5728\n\n```\nls -ld /data\n```\n\n\u6b63\u5e38\u793a\u4f8b\uff1a\n\n```\ndrwxr-xr-x 3 root root 4096 /data\n```\n\n------\n\n## \u4e09\u3001\u5b89\u88c5 Samba\uff08\u4ece\u7cfb\u7edf\u5c42\u5f00\u59cb\uff09\n\n### 3.1 \u5b89\u88c5 Samba\n\n```\nsudo apt update\nsudo apt install -y samba\n```\n\n\u5b89\u88c5\u5b8c\u6210\u540e\uff0c\u7cfb\u7edf\u4f1a\u81ea\u52a8\u542f\u52a8\u670d\u52a1\u3002", "top": 0, "createdAt": 1770172911, "style": "", "script": "<script src='https://blog.meekdai.com/Gmeek/plugins/articletoc.js'></script><script src='https://blog.meekdai.com/Gmeek/plugins/lightbox.js'></script>", "head": "", "ogImage": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/103094747?s=400&u=54690c656e8bf740633710628214ac5a495f4838&v=4", "createdDate": "2026-02-04", "dateLabelColor": "#1f883d"}, "P11": {"htmlDir": "docs/post/11.html", "labels": ["softwares"], "postTitle": "\u4ece\u96f6\u5f00\u59cb\u7684\u5c0f\u4e3b\u673a\u6298\u817e\u8bb0#5 \u2014\u2014\u6587\u4ef6\u8fc1\u79fb\uff08NTFS\uff09", "postUrl": "post/11.html", "postSourceUrl": "https://github.com/10086Coda10086/10086Coda10086.github.io/issues/11", "commentNum": 0, "wordCount": 2277, "description": "**\u63d2\u76d8 \u2192 \u6302\u8f7d NTFS \u2192 \u62f7\u8d1d \u2192 \u5b89\u5168\u5378\u8f7d**\n\n## \u4e00\u3001\u7269\u7406\u63d2\u76d8\u540e\u5148\u786e\u8ba4\u8bbe\u5907\u540d\uff08\u975e\u5e38\u5173\u952e\uff09\n\n\u63d2\u4e0a **NTFS \u786c\u76d8** \u540e\uff0c\u4e0d\u8981\u6025\u7740\u6302\u8f7d\uff0c\u5148\u786e\u8ba4\u5b83\u662f\u54ea\u4e2a\u76d8\u3002", "top": 0, "createdAt": 1770198876, "style": "", "script": "<script src='https://blog.meekdai.com/Gmeek/plugins/articletoc.js'></script><script src='https://blog.meekdai.com/Gmeek/plugins/lightbox.js'></script>", "head": "", "ogImage": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/103094747?s=400&u=54690c656e8bf740633710628214ac5a495f4838&v=4", "createdDate": "2026-02-04", "dateLabelColor": "#1f883d"}, "P12": {"htmlDir": "docs/post/12.html", "labels": ["softwares"], "postTitle": "\u4ece\u96f6\u5f00\u59cb\u7684\u5c0f\u4e3b\u673a\u6298\u817e\u8bb0#6  \u2014\u2014Docker\u8fdb\u9636", "postUrl": "post/12.html", "postSourceUrl": "https://github.com/10086Coda10086/10086Coda10086.github.io/issues/12", "commentNum": 0, "wordCount": 3870, "description": "## 1. \u5b89\u88c5\u9762\u677f**Portainer**\n\n**\u5b9a\u4f4d**\uff1a\u6700\u5e38\u7528\u7684 Docker \u56fe\u5f62\u5316\u7ba1\u7406\u9762\u677f\n**\u9002\u7528\u573a\u666f**\uff1a\u65b0\u624b + \u4e2d\u9ad8\u7ea7\u7528\u6237\u90fd\u5408\u9002\n\n### \u4f18\u70b9\n\n- \u7b80\u6d01\u3001\u6613\u4e0a\u624b\n- \u80fd\u7ba1\u7406\u672c\u673a Docker \u4ee5\u53ca\u8fdc\u7a0b Docker\n- \u652f\u6301 Stack / Compose\n- \u5185\u7f6e\u5e94\u7528\u6a21\u677f\uff08\u5feb\u901f\u90e8\u7f72\u670d\u52a1\uff09\n- \u793e\u533a\u6d3b\u8dc3\n\n### \u7f3a\u70b9\n\n- \u9ed8\u8ba4\u65e0\u9700\u590d\u6742 RBAC\uff08\u6743\u9650\u7ba1\u7406\uff09\u65f6\u4f53\u9a8c\u6700\u597d\n- \u6808\u7ba1\u7406\u4e0d\u5982 Swarm/Kubernetes \u5f3a\u5927\n\n### \u5b89\u88c5\u6781\u7b80\u793a\u4f8b\uff08Docker\uff09\n\n```\ndocker run -d \\\n  -p 9000:9000 \\\n  -v /var/run/docker.sock:/var/run/docker.sock \\\n  -v portainer_data:/data \\\n  portainer/portainer-ce:latest\n```\n\n\u8bbf\u95ee\u7aef\u53e3\uff1a\n\n```\nhttp://\u670d\u52a1\u5668IP:9000\n```\n\n---\n\n## 2. \u5b89\u88c5Transmission\n\n### 1\ufe0f\u20e3 \u521b\u5efa\u4e0b\u8f7d\u76ee\u5f55\n\n\u4f60\u5df2\u7ecf\u628a `sdb` \u6302\u8f7d\u5230 `/data` \u4e0b\uff0c\u6211\u4eec\u4e3a Transmission \u521b\u5efa\u4e13\u7528\u76ee\u5f55\uff1a\n\n```\nsudo mkdir -p /data/transmission/config\nsudo mkdir -p /data/transmission/downloads\nsudo chown -R lluosu:lluosu /data/transmission\n```\n\n- `config` \u5b58\u653e Transmission \u914d\u7f6e\u6587\u4ef6\n- `downloads` \u5b58\u653e\u4e0b\u8f7d\u7684\u6587\u4ef6\n- \u6743\u9650\u8bbe\u7f6e\u4e3a\u4f60\u81ea\u5df1\u7684\u7528\u6237\uff0c\u907f\u514d Docker \u8bbf\u95ee\u6743\u9650\u95ee\u9898\n\n------\n\n### 2\ufe0f\u20e3 \u7f16\u5199 Docker Compose \u6587\u4ef6\n\n\u5728\u4f60\u7684\u4e3b\u76ee\u5f55\u4e0b\u521b\u5efa\u4e00\u4e2a\u6587\u4ef6\u5939\u5b58\u653e docker-compose \u6587\u4ef6\uff0c\u4f8b\u5982\uff1a\n\n```\nmkdir -p ~/docker/transmission\ncd ~/docker/transmission\n```\n\n\u521b\u5efa `docker-compose.yml`\uff1a\n\n```\nversion: '3.9'\nservices:\n  transmission:\n    image: linuxserver/transmission\n    container_name: transmission\n    environment:\n      - PUID=1000              # \u4f60\u7684 Linux \u7528\u6237 ID\n      - PGID=1000              # \u4f60\u7684 Linux \u7528\u6237\u7ec4 ID\n      - TZ=Asia/Shanghai       # \u65f6\u533a\n    volumes:\n      - /data/transmission/config:/config\n      - /data/transmission/downloads:/downloads\n    ports:\n      - 9091:9091   # Web UI\n      - 51413:51413 # BitTorrent TCP\n      - 51413:51413/udp # BitTorrent UDP\n    restart: unless-stopped\n```\n\n> \u6ce8\u610f\uff1a\n>\n> - `PUID` \u548c `PGID` \u7528 `id lluosu` \u67e5\u770b\u4f60\u7684\u7528\u6237\u548c\u7ec4 ID\n> - \u7aef\u53e3\u53ef\u4ee5\u6309\u9700\u8981\u6539\uff0c\u5982\u679c 9091 \u88ab\u5360\u7528\uff0c\u53ef\u4ee5\u6362\u6210 9092:9091\n\n------\n\n### 3\ufe0f\u20e3 \u542f\u52a8\u5bb9\u5668\n\n\u8fdb\u5165 `docker-compose.yml` \u6240\u5728\u76ee\u5f55\uff0c\u6267\u884c\uff1a\n\n```\ndocker compose up -d\n```\n\n\u68c0\u67e5\u5bb9\u5668\u72b6\u6001\uff1a\n\n```\ndocker ps\n```\n\n\u4f60\u5e94\u8be5\u770b\u5230 `transmission` \u6b63\u5728\u8fd0\u884c\u3002", "top": 0, "createdAt": 1770198909, "style": "", "script": "<script src='https://blog.meekdai.com/Gmeek/plugins/articletoc.js'></script><script src='https://blog.meekdai.com/Gmeek/plugins/lightbox.js'></script>", "head": "", "ogImage": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/103094747?s=400&u=54690c656e8bf740633710628214ac5a495f4838&v=4", "createdDate": "2026-02-04", "dateLabelColor": "#1f883d"}, "P13": {"htmlDir": "docs/post/13.html", "labels": ["Post"], "postTitle": "\u8db5\u7a81\u6cc9", "postUrl": "post/13.html", "postSourceUrl": "https://github.com/10086Coda10086/10086Coda10086.github.io/issues/13", "commentNum": 0, "wordCount": 1738, "description": "\u5feb\u5230\u4e86\u3002", "top": 0, "createdAt": 1771475537, "style": "", "script": "<script src='https://blog.meekdai.com/Gmeek/plugins/articletoc.js'></script><script src='https://blog.meekdai.com/Gmeek/plugins/lightbox.js'></script>", "head": "", "ogImage": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/103094747?s=400&u=54690c656e8bf740633710628214ac5a495f4838&v=4", "createdDate": "2026-02-19", "dateLabelColor": "#1f883d"}, "P14": {"htmlDir": "docs/post/14.html", "labels": ["documentation", "softwares"], "postTitle": "shadowrocket\u4f7f\u7528\u624b\u518c\uff08\u642c\u8fd0\uff09", "postUrl": "post/14.html", "postSourceUrl": "https://github.com/10086Coda10086/10086Coda10086.gi